tring\">'__subclasshook__'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'__weakref__'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'balance'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'deposit'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n <span class=\"token string\">'inquiry'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'num_accounts'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'withdraw'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>References</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://index-of.co.uk/Python/Python%20Essential%20Reference,%20Fourth%20Edition.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Python Essential Reference</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"py/classes/scope","previousSlug":"py/classes/instance","nextSlug":"py/classes/inheritance","previousTitle":"Class Instances","nextTitle":"Inheritance"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}